# Documentation language

- **All project documentation must be written in English only.**
- This includes: README, AGENTS.md, RULE.md, doc comments, user-facing help text, and any other documentation or instructional content added to the project.
- Do **not** add documentation in French or in any other non-English language.
- Code identifiers (variables, functions, file names) and commit messages may follow project conventions (e.g. conventional commits); the language rule applies to prose and user-facing documentation.
